# id: MesosConfiguration -> public static void logMesosConfig(Logger log, MesosConfiguration config)
commentText: A utility method to log relevant Mesos connection info
codeText: public static void logMesosConfig(Logger log, MesosConfiguration config) {__		Map<String,String> env = System.getenv()__		Protos.FrameworkInfo.Builder info = config.frameworkInfo()___		log.info("--------------------------------------------------------------------------------")__		log.info(" Mesos Info:")__		log.info("    Master URL: {}", config.masterUrl())___		log.info(" Framework Info:")__		log.info("    ID: {}", info.hasId() ? info.getId().getValue() : "(none)")__		log.info("    Name: {}", info.hasName() ? info.getName() : "(none)")__		log.info("    Failover Timeout (secs): {}", info.getFailoverTimeout())__		log.info("    Role: {}", info.hasRole() ? info.getRole() : "(none)")__		log.info("    Principal: {}", info.hasPrincipal() ? info.getPrincipal() : "(none)")__		log.info("    Host: {}", info.hasHostname() ? info.getHostname() : "(none)")__		if(env.containsKey("LIBPROCESS_IP")) {_			log.info("    LIBPROCESS_IP: {}", env.get("LIBPROCESS_IP"))__		}_		if(env.containsKey("LIBPROCESS_PORT")) {_			log.info("    LIBPROCESS_PORT: {}", env.get("LIBPROCESS_PORT"))__		}_		log.info("    Web UI: {}", info.hasWebuiUrl() ? info.getWebuiUrl() : "(none)")___		log.info("--------------------------------------------------------------------------------")___	}
